<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 06:15:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>马尔代夫总统因与印度关系恶化而吸引中国投资者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-president-courts-investors-china-ties-with-india-sag-2024-01-09/</link><description>在中国南部港口城市举行的“投资马尔代夫”论坛上，马尔代夫总统与微笑的当地官员握手并交谈，此次中国之行旨在深化双边关系，因为这个群岛国家正在远离印度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 05:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-president-courts-investors-china-ties-with-india-sag-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪将于下周在印度尼西亚推出汽车 - 公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launch-cars-indonesia-next-week-company-2024-01-09/</link><description>中国比亚迪公司周二表示，全球最大的纯电动汽车 (BEV) 销售商将于下周在印度尼西亚推出其汽车。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 05:28:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launch-cars-indonesia-next-week-company-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>不丹在最后一轮全国选举中投票，经济是主要问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bhutan-votes-final-round-national-elections-economy-main-issue-2024-01-09/</link><description>不丹于周二开始投票，这是最后一轮全国议会选举，该选举将组建喜马拉雅王国自 15 年前建立民主以来的第四届政府，经济增长是新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫情后的主要问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bhutan-votes-final-round-national-elections-economy-main-issue-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>香港领导人表示国泰航空需要解决运力问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-needs-address-capacity-issues-hong-kong-leader-says-2024-01-09/</link><description>香港领导人表示，香港国泰航空计划在繁忙的农历新年期间削减航班，这表明该航空公司需要解决运力问题，而其飞行员工会则呼吁政府进行调查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:22:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-needs-address-capacity-issues-hong-kong-leader-says-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 所有者字节跳动正在与腾讯等公司洽谈出售游戏资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tiktok-owner-bytedance-talks-with-tencent-others-sell-gaming-assets-2024-01-09/</link><description>TikTok 母公司字节跳动周二表示，随着这家中国社交媒体公司退出游戏行业，该公司正在与其游戏资产的多个潜在买家进行谈判，其中包括全球最大的视频游戏公司腾讯。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 02:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tiktok-owner-bytedance-talks-with-tencent-others-sell-gaming-assets-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>全球投资者等待美国通胀数据，亚洲股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-09/</link><description>周二，在科技股引领华尔街股市飙升之后，亚洲股指大多走高，因投资者等待本周公布的下一组美国通胀数据，这可能暗示美联储何时可能开始降息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 01:40:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>台湾执政党候选人将维持现状与中国接触</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ruling-party-candidate-will-maintain-status-quo-engage-with-china-2024-01-09/</link><description>台湾执政党总统候选人赖清德周二表示，如果当选，他将维持现状并通过实力追求和平，并在平等和尊严的前提下对与北京接触保持开放态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 01:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ruling-party-candidate-will-maintain-status-quo-engage-with-china-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>台湾国防部称在台湾海峡上空看到四个中国气球</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defence-ministry-says-it-saw-four-chinese-balloons-over-taiwan-strait-2024-01-09/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，周一在台湾海峡上空发现了四个中国气球，其中两个气球飞越了台湾岛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 01:11:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defence-ministry-says-it-saw-four-chinese-balloons-over-taiwan-strait-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>美元回落，比特币在 ETF 批准截止日期前上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-pulls-back-bitcoin-jumps-ahead-etf-approval-deadline-2024-01-09/</link><description>美元周二暂停涨势，交易员重申了对美联储今年一系列降息的押注，因为他们相信美国通胀已充分放缓。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 00:53:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-pulls-back-bitcoin-jumps-ahead-etf-approval-deadline-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国海军水手因与中国分享军事数据被判入狱27个月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-navy-sailor-given-27-months-jail-sharing-military-data-with-china-2024-01-08/</link><description>周一，一名美国海军水兵因收受一名中国情报官员近 15,000 美元的贿赂以换取美国非机密私人军事信息的照片而被判处 27 个月监禁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 22:03:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-navy-sailor-given-27-months-jail-sharing-military-data-with-china-2024-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲 东京交易员将了解通胀数据并等待美国消费者物价指数 (CPI)</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-08/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 21:49:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达扩大在中国电动汽车领域的影响力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-expands-its-reach-chinas-ev-sector-2024-01-08/</link><description>英伟达表示，四个中国电动汽车品牌将使用其技术作为自动驾驶系统的大脑，这突显了这家美国芯片制造商尽管华盛顿实施更严格的出口规定，仍决心在中国扩张。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 16:44:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-expands-its-reach-chinas-ev-sector-2024-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>法国干邑白兰地生产商反击中国反倾销调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/french-cognac-makers-hit-back-chinese-anti-dumping-probe-2024-01-08/</link><description>法国干邑白兰地生产商对中国有关他们在中国市场倾销白兰地的说法进行了反击，称所称的价格折扣对于此类正式调查而言异常小。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/french-cognac-makers-hit-back-chinese-anti-dumping-probe-2024-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>STATBOX 足球-亚洲杯 B 组 - 澳大利亚、乌兹别克斯坦、叙利亚、印度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/statbox-soccer-asian-cup-group-b-australia-uzbekistan-syria-india-2024-01-08/</link><description>亚洲杯 B 组 Statbox 将于 1 月 12 日至 2 月 10 日在卡塔尔举行：</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:14:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/statbox-soccer-asian-cup-group-b-australia-uzbekistan-syria-india-2024-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国堵住地方政府离岸融资漏洞——消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-lgfvs-stop-issuing-offshore-364-day-bonds-sources-2024-01-08/</link><description>四位知情人士告诉路透社，中国监管机构去年堵住了一个监管漏洞，该漏洞允许负债累累的地方政府融资平台（LGFV）进一步增加借款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-lgfvs-stop-issuing-offshore-364-day-bonds-sources-2024-01-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>